<item>
            <title>[SOLR-5048] fail the build if the example solrconfig.xml files don&apos;t have an up to date luceneMatchVersion</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5048</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;4.4 RC0 still had &lt;tt&gt;&amp;lt;luceneMatchVersion&amp;gt;LUCENE_43&amp;lt;/luceneMatchVersion&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt; ... the build should fail in a situation like this.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <environment></environment>
